<item><title>Montesa, Yehl Selected on Day 1 of MLB Draft</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/7/11/baseball-montesa-yehl-selected-on-day-1-of-mlb-draft</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/7/11/baseball-montesa-yehl-selected-on-day-1-of-mlb-draft</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Dawson Montesa, Maxx Yehl" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/7/11/Untitled-1Montesa__Yeh.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – West Virginia University pitchers Dawson Montesa and Maxx Yehl became the latest Mountaineers to be selected in the MLB Draft on Saturday. Montesa was taken by the St. Louis Cardinals in the Competitive Balance-B round with the 72nd overall pick while Yehl was selected in the third round by the Kansas City Royals with the 91st overall pick.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/11/Untitled-1Montesa__Yeh.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/11/Untitled-1Montesa__Yeh.jpg"><media:title>Dawson Montesa, Maxx Yehl</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/11/Untitled-1Montesa__Yeh.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Sat, 11 Jul 2026 19:29:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59237</s:story_id></item><item><title>Jacksonville State Transfer Cook Expected to Boost Mountaineer Ground Game</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/7/10/football-jacksonville-state-transfer-cook-expected-to-boost-mountaineer-ground-game</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/7/10/football-jacksonville-state-transfer-cook-expected-to-boost-mountaineer-ground-game</guid><category>Football</category